android 8.0

app启动流程：
Android系统在启动过程中，首先会在用户空间启动init进程，然后启动zygote进程，zygote接着fork出ServerManager进程，
ServerManager进程启动完成后，会接着启动system_server进程，system_server进程中会启动AMS，WMS等framework的服务，
并将这些服务的binder句柄添加到到ServerManager中维护，最后启动Launcher这个应用进程

Launcher  ->(Binder)   SystemServer(AMS)   ->(Socket)   ->   Zygote
->   fock   ->   app   ->   启动ActivityThread的main()方法
->   方法里执行ActivityThread thread = new ActivityThread()   ->
->   thread.attach()   ->   IActivityManager.attachApplication()又回到了AMS
->   AMS.bindApplication()   ->   ApplicationThread发送H.BIND_APPLICATION
->   ActivityThread.handleBindApplication()


Activity启动流程：
1.Activity   ->   startActivity()   ->   startActivityForResult()   ->     mInstrumentation.execStartActivity
2.Instrumentation   ->   ActivityManager.getService().startActivity()

3.ActivityManagerService(IActivityManager.Stub的实现类)   ->   startActivityAsUser()   ->   ActivityTaskManagerService.startActivityAsUser()
4.ActivityTaskManagerService   ->   ActivityStarter.startActivityMayWait()
.
